---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactUs from '../components/ContactUs.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Glob">
	<div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto">
		<!-- Row 1: 3 Image Gallery -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 p-4 max-md:grid-cols-1">
			<div class="p-4">
				<img src="/images/pic5.png" alt="" class="w-full h-auto align-top" />
			</div>
			<div class="p-4">
				<img src="/images/pic4.png" alt="" class="w-full h-auto align-top" />
			</div>
			<div class="p-4">
				<img src="/images/pic8.png" alt="" class="w-full h-auto align-top" />
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Row 2: Text Content Box -->
		<div class="p-4">
			<div class="bg-[#4b4e52] p-8 text-center">
				<div class="text-glob-text">
					<p class="text-[20pt] leading-[40px] font-bold mb-4">RURAL HEALTH CHECKS</p>
					<p class="text-[16pt] leading-[32px] mb-4">Making it happen. Bringing the Glob to our faming communities and their families. Showing them that we really care about their welfare and health. We have the manpower and expertise to this, and we have the drive to make this happen.</p>
					<p class="text-[16pt] leading-[32px] text-left">Rural health checks will save lives. It will change the attitude of farmers and their families to the importance of self-care. Farmers often know the importance of having their machinery serviced every year. Unfortunately, they do not recognize of including themselves in this check list.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Row 3: Banner Image -->
		<div class="p-2.5">
			<img src="/images/Picture8.png" alt="" class="w-full max-w-[920px] mx-auto h-auto align-top" />
		</div>
		
		<!-- Row 4: 3 Column Layout with Gradient -->
		<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-glob-orange to-white p-4">
			<!-- Desktop: 3 columns -->
			<div class="hidden md:grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center">
				<div class="p-2.5">
					<img src="/images/Dean_lvn3vtne.png" alt="" class="w-full max-w-[280px] mx-auto h-auto align-top" />
				</div>
				<div class="p-2.5 text-center">
					<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[28px] font-bold mb-4 text-[#434343]">....from Dean Williamson</p>
					<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[28px] font-bold mb-4 text-[#434343]">This article was taken from Dean's facebook page. It gives us some insight to where it started and the need for this project.</p>
					<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[28px]"><a href="/deanwilliamson" class="text-black underline">Click here</a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-2.5">
					<img src="/images/HQlogo.png" alt="" class="w-full max-w-[280px] mx-auto h-auto align-top" />
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Mobile: Stacked order - text first, then images -->
			<div class="md:hidden flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
				<div class="p-2.5 text-center order-1">
					<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[28px] font-bold mb-4 text-[#434343]">....from Dean Williamson</p>
					<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[28px] font-bold mb-4 text-[#434343]">This article was taken from Dean's facebook page. It gives us some insight to where it started and the need for this project.</p>
					<p class="text-[14pt] leading-[28px]"><a href="/deanwilliamson" class="text-black underline">Click here</a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-2.5 order-2">
					<img src="/images/HQlogo.png" alt="" class="w-full max-w-[280px] mx-auto h-auto align-top" />
				</div>
				<div class="p-2.5 order-3">
					<img src="/images/Dean_lvn3vtne.png" alt="" class="w-full max-w-[280px] mx-auto h-auto align-top" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Row 5: Feedback Text -->
		<div class="p-2.5">
			<p class="text-[16pt] leading-[28px] text-white">Over the last two years the glob has seen hundreds of working farmers (with their boots on!) The feed back from the participants and their families has been incredibly positive with many messages of thanks coming back to us for what this project has done.</p>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Row 6: Lions Emblem and Agri HQ Text -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-[160px_1fr] gap-4 items-center p-2.5 max-md:grid-cols-1">
			<div class="flex items-center justify-center">
				<img src="/images/LCI_emblem_2color_web.png" alt="" class="w-full max-w-[160px] h-auto align-top" />
			</div>
			<div class="p-2.5">
				<p class="text-[16pt] leading-[28px] text-white font-[Calibri]">Agri HQ have 'gifted' Zone One 202D the glob. They recognise that NZ Lions is respected in the community and has a club in every town. Approx. 25% of our members are farmers.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Row 7: Contact Link -->
		<ContactUs />
	</div>
</Layout>
